The paradox with the new US administration is that Joe Biden is not that guy.He has calmly added seasoned experts and experienced thinkers to his various teams. So America has a new president, and wherever I look, I see news about the new administration’s plans and programmes.
The Biden immigration plan. The Biden climate policy. The Biden antitrust approach. The Biden anti-Covid programme. The Biden economic stimulus.
What’s wrong with that, you ask? The word BIDEN!



